deck: Concept Artist, Colorist, Illustrator. Member of Manfont.
description:
Giorgia Lanza (school '94) graduated at the "International Comic Art School" of Turin with excellent grades, and she's also completed the Concept Art Master organized by "Big Rock, Institute of Magic Technologies".

She's been working as a colorist for 3 years. Her first publication was Agenzia Investigativa Carlo Lorenzini issue #1 (2014) and then issue #2 (2015), published by Manfont Comics. She's colored Damsels in Excess issue # 5 (2015) published by Zenescope. She's illustated two books for private clients. Right now she's working on two projects that will be released and distributed at Lucca Comics&Games 2016: illustrations for a rpg card game called Drops of memory (published by Acchiappasogni) and Hotline Miami_Wildlife issue #3 (published by Saldapress).
name: Giorgia Lanza
